# 🧱 1. Template Spring Batch "production-ready"

## ✅ Configuration de base

```java
@Configuration
@EnableBatchProcessing
public class BatchConfig {

    @Bean
    public Job cleanDataJob(JobRepository jobRepository, Step cleanStep) {
        return new JobBuilder("clean-data-job", jobRepository)
                .incrementer(new RunIdIncrementer()) // restart safe
                .start(cleanStep)
                .build();
    }

    @Bean
    public Step cleanStep(JobRepository jobRepository,
                          PlatformTransactionManager transactionManager,
                          ItemReader<MyEntity> reader,
                          ItemProcessor<MyEntity, MyEntity> processor,
                          ItemWriter<MyEntity> writer) {

        return new StepBuilder("clean-step", jobRepository)
                .<MyEntity, MyEntity>chunk(1000, transactionManager)
                .reader(reader)
                .processor(processor)
                .writer(writer)
                .faultTolerant()
                .skip(InvalidDataException.class)
                .skipLimit(100)
                .retry(SQLException.class)
                .retryLimit(3)
                .build();
    }
}
```

